com.nexmo.sdk.core.client

Class ResultCodes

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nexmo.sdk.core.client.ResultCodes

  • public class ResultCodes
extends java.lang.Object
    Internal error codes sent by the SDK service. They describe an unrecoverable error.
